    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the COU is explicitly scoped to the ASTM F1717 single-angle compression-bending configuration, and the regulatory submission does not extrapolate to other load angles. The E/uval metric is satisfied for all QoIs across all three ensemble models. The package conforms to ProfileMinimal; a digital signature has not yet been applied pending completion of the institutional signature workflow. The hash field provides content integrity verification in the interim.",
